    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The measure or distance of the extent across a surface. For the length of a straight horizontal line extending from one side to the other of a form, prefer "width," although usage overlaps.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
